19
00:01:31,291 --> 00:01:35,535
But who knows what the results of this
little fishing expedition may be.

20
00:02:38,558 --> 00:02:41,198
What a beautiful spot.
Yes.

21
00:02:41,661 --> 00:02:43,504
But it certainly
was strange, dear.

22
00:02:43,563 --> 00:02:47,636
