off the beach just as we arrived.

23
00:02:48,768 --> 00:02:52,739
Well, it's probably just another
one of those jellyfish scares.

24
00:02:58,711 --> 00:03:00,850
Herman, where are you going?

25
00:03:00,914 --> 00:03:01,915
