digging me up like last time.

35
00:03:42,388 --> 00:03:44,425
<i>(announcer) That Russian trawler
spotted off our coast...</i>

36
00:03:44,490 --> 00:03:46,834
<i>is still in the vicinity
of Paradise Cove.</i>

37
00:03:46,893 --> 00:03:50,739
<i>They have their nets out and they are
still beyond the three-mile limit.</i>

38
00:03:50,863 --> 00:03:53,173
<i>Well, good fishing, comrades.</i>

39
