You speak English!

92
00:07:43,729 --> 00:07:44,730
[exclaims]

93
00:07:45,431 --> 00:07:47,604
Well, isn't it
a small world.

94
00:07:47,667 --> 00:07:49,476
Yes, I speak English.

95
00:07:49,535 --> 00:07:51,173
Me speak English.

96
00:07:51,237 --> 00:07:52,910
Me speak English.

