[speaking Russian]

104
00:08:19,866 --> 00:08:24,008
You very valuable
anthropological find.

105
00:08:25,137 --> 00:08:26,480
Thank you.

106
00:08:27,139 --> 00:08:28,641
I do my best.

107
00:08:33,779 --> 00:08:35,087
[giggling]

108
