111
00:08:53,065 --> 00:08:55,705
What has four wheels
and flies?

112
00:08:56,335 --> 00:08:57,336
[chuckling]

113
00:08:59,038 --> 00:09:01,177
Could be new secret weapon.

114
00:09:01,374 --> 00:09:02,751
