has four wheels and flies?"

116
00:09:07,046 --> 00:09:08,923
Okay, sea monster.

117
00:09:09,315 --> 00:09:12,319
What has four wheels
and flies?

118
00:09:13,386 --> 00:09:14,990
A garbage truck.

119
00:09:16,022 --> 00:09:17,729
A garbage truck?

