[all laughing]

122
00:09:24,897 --> 00:09:27,104
[speaking Russian]

123
00:09:35,141 --> 00:09:38,520
Say, listen.
You're a very good group.

124
00:09:39,278 --> 00:09:42,191
Here's another one
that'll really grab you.

125
00:09:56,162 --> 00:09:58,142
Trawler number 47.

126
