Hold it.

160
00:11:55,314 --> 00:11:57,157
I think
I'm getting something now.

161
00:11:57,216 --> 00:11:59,753
What is it?
I see an ocean.

162
00:12:00,252 --> 00:12:02,323
I see a boat.
Do you see Pop?

163
00:12:02,922 --> 00:12:05,596
Now hold it.
It's coming in clear now.

164
00:12:06,092 --> 00:12:09,266
There he is. I see Herman.
What's he doing?

165
00:12:09,328 --> 00:12:10,966
He's on a ship...

166
00:12:11,430 --> 00:12:15,742
and he is leading up a bunch of
funny-looking men in community singing.

167
00:12:16,902 --> 00:12:18,643
That's ridiculous.

168
00:12:18,938 --> 00:12:21,817
But, Lily, I saw it.
It was right there.

169
00:12:22,341 --> 00:12:24,446
That crystal ball
has never been the same...

170
00:12:24,510 --> 00:12:28,151
since Spot sat on it for three
days and tried to hatch it.

