190
00:13:20,399 --> 00:13:23,005
Why? What's the matter?
Was I off-key?

191
00:13:23,068 --> 00:13:25,708
I just contact Moscow
on the wireless.

192
00:13:26,172 --> 00:13:28,584
Do you know
what you are, Herman?

193
00:13:29,041 --> 00:13:30,384
What I am?

194
00:13:31,377 --> 00:13:34,324
I get it. It's gonna
be one of those jokes.

195
