"No such person exists."

229
00:15:23,322 --> 00:15:25,962
Look, they have
Pop's picture in the paper.

230
00:15:26,025 --> 00:15:27,766
That's my Herman.

231
00:15:28,460 --> 00:15:31,373
That Russian trawler we heard
about on the radio.

232
00:15:31,430 --> 00:15:33,376
They must have
picked up Herman.

233
00:15:33,432 --> 00:15:36,743
How could a grown man go out
for a harmless little swim...

234
00:15:36,802 --> 00:15:39,840
and wind up being captured
by the Russians as a spy?

235
00:15:39,905 --> 00:15:42,852
I'll admit it's difficult,
but in all the world...

236
00:15:42,908 --> 00:15:46,754
only my son-in-law has the talent
to do anything that stupid.

237
00:15:54,219 --> 00:15:56,426
"Russian spy story a fake."

238
00:15:57,022 --> 00:16:01,528
